New year refers to the time period starting from January 1st, 2023; 
Tag count represents the number of tags assigned to each feature;
The question aims to identify popular features by their tag counts.

sql:
SELECT feature_name, description
FROM features
WHERE feature_id IN (SELECT DISTINCT feature_id FROM feature_requests);

SELECT feature_id, AVG(average_response_time) AS avg_response_time
FROM feature_metrics
GROUP BY feature_id;

SELECT AVG(error_rate) as average_error_rate
FROM feature_metrics
WHERE feature_id = 1;

SELECT feature_id, average_response_time, error_rate
FROM feature_metrics
ORDER BY average_response_time ASC;

SELECT status
FROM feature_requests
WHERE request_id = 1;

SELECT DISTINCT feature_id
FROM user_feedback
WHERE rating > 4;
